ILI TECHNOLOGY June Sales Rise 29.33% (Table) : 3598 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-07-06T09:52:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/ili-technology-june-sales-rise-29-33-table-3598-tt.html
ILI TECHNOLOGY said unconsolidated sales
in June rose 29.33% to NT$545,913,000 from NT$422,099,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            545,913          422,099    
YOY%              29.33%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           3,659,443        2,539,845   
YOY%              44.08% 
=================================================================
 